{"type": "article", "id": 3283, "title": "Eley Kishimoto & Fossil 手表", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-05T08:33:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232945GFjTCyq3YKQNAeak.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦时尚品牌 Eley Kishimoto 日前联手美国生活时尚品牌 Fossil 推出了一款名为 Retro Timer 的手表，其设计灵感来源于 1950 年代的厨房计时器，与如今市面上的多数手表， Retro Timer 有一个不寻常的计时机制，一根指针用来标注小时，中间可旋转的红色铝制圆盘则代替了分针与秒针的功能。Retro Timer 采用皮质表带，男女皆宜，提供蓝绿色表盘／白色表带、白色表盘／棕色表带以及黑色表盘／黑色表带 3 种配色，定价 129.17 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/retro-timer-white-brown/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232941zFaIoYf8etEHCMsP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232941XHEkTU5ImuDSV0dA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232942Pg9R3q6ABMzb2oWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232942e7yLMrUb5ndc3PCk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232943T4Z21ujthyMYUC5A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232943tsSpqUNzofXGQvk2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}